    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Shane Guerette"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "<p><strong>MRG Presale:</strong> February 25 @ 11:00 AM ET<br><strong>On Sale:</strong> February 27 @ 11:00 AM ET<br><br>It&rsquo;s the old way of doing things that inspires a new sound for upstate NY-based artist, Shane Guerrette. Drawing influence from classic soul and roots rock genres, Shane has only just begun to craft his own retro-flavored sound. Having self-produced two albums since 2022, a considerable buzz amongst industry and fans alike has been built -leading to millions of streams, multiple tours and festival appearances. Since the start of 2023, Shane and his band have toured relentlessly, opening up for acts such as The Heavy Heavy, Black Pistol Fire, Neal Francis, The Sheepdogs, The Wood Brothers, Black Joe Lewis, &amp; The Stone Foxes as well as playing at major festivals such as Mountain Jam, Rhythm and Roots, Winnetka, and Alternating Currents. With a third album due out later in 2025, you&rsquo;re going to want to keep an eye on what&rsquo;s next for this rising star.<br><br><strong>Have an MRG Credit/Gift Card? Redeem for tickets&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://mrglive-redeem.square.site/s/shop\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"a\"><strong>HERE</strong></a></p>"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventStatus": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/EventScheduled"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/eventAttendanceMode": [
      {
        "@id": "http://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode"
      }
    ]
  },
